    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend_Form documentation, at 15.2.6:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        if (!$form-&gt;isValid($_POST)) {
            // Failed validation; redisplay form
            $this-&gt;form = $form;
            return $this-&gt;render('form');
        }
</code></pre>

<p>I think it's:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        if (!$form-&gt;isValid($_POST)) {
            // Failed validation; redisplay form
            $this-&gt;view-&gt;form = $form;
            return $this-&gt;render('form');
        }
</code></pre>

